snippet.title: Protocore - PRE ALPHA TRAILER
snippet.description:
JOIN THE COMMUNITY ON DISCORD : https://protocore.fr/discord

PROTOCORE is a blood-pumping, nerve-wracking arcade shooter where you’ll fight your
way across a randomly generated spaceship. Fight alone or with your friends to learn who
you are and who wants you dead. Shoot your way through an army of robots sent after
you and turn them into a pile of smoldering metal.

More info on https://protocore.fr
